      from recording with DevTools attached; real app JS is 20ms.
    • Forced synchronous layout detected — 8 reflows, 2ms — but the run-up is dominated by
      a browser DevTools extension (measureHostInstance) reading component geometry: a
      capture artifact that won't occur in production. Re-capture with DevTools detached
      to measure your app's own forced reflow.

